            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann4" ANNOTATION_REF="ann2_flexid_96c14b2e-6a18-42ac-aa4e-4b716af5fb06">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>The name of the village, I work presently, is Zubi.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann145" ANNOTATION_REF="ann143_flexid_48844f9f-948e-42ed-a45c-02f478e1554c">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>As for the origin of the word, it is not difficult to guess. It should have occurred after the Russian invasion. The territory, where the village is located presently, was a bank of the Khobistskali river.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann553" ANNOTATION_REF="ann551_flexid_4928ebd0-2997-45e8-aa7f-a8b663f6c3f8">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>That is, there was no settlement.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann610" ANNOTATION_REF="ann608_flexid_ca34ebe4-35f1-4be2-a854-7be636f641d5">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>A man going with his cart and saw a trouble Russian running, and, when he asked what was happening to him, the answer was: "Zub, Zub." It appeared that he suffered from tooth-ache.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1088" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1086_flexid_37f0693c-42a2-4292-a478-0d676248ec86">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>But, in those times, nobody in the village spoke Russian, and the carter didn't give him a hand of help.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1337" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1335_flexid_273b186d-97a7-475c-90dc-5b23c959c6c2">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>However, the name Zubi, as a foreign word, was eventually given to the neighborhood where my fellow villagers live presently.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1595" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1593_flexid_0e95f1cc-ada9-40f8-93d1-929f7a6f952b">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>There is a school in Zubi.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1659" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1657_flexid_bb65b0c4-71e1-4aac-885e-97baab6eeffc">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>There is a shop where we come together.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1731" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1729_flexid_592da25b-98e9-4e43-b2ad-b146657ad36d">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>In the past, we had a pharmacy as well; however, it doesn't have enough customaers and it was closed.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1909" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1907_flexid_ff20def0-f051-491f-9617-297c09fb5d7d">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Everything what pertains to Georgian customs is performed in the village.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann2079" ANNOTATION_REF="ann2077_flexid_223b9763-1c4e-458e-8538-c2ca5ff9217e">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>We celebrate New Year's Day, Christmas.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
    </TIER>
    <TIER LANG_REF="ka-Brai" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="phrase-item"
        PARENT_REF="A_phrase-txt-xmf" TIER_ID="A_phrase-gls-ka-Brai">
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann5" ANNOTATION_REF="ann2_flexid_96c14b2e-6a18-42ac-aa4e-4b716af5fb06">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>თვითონ [ამ სოფელს], სადაც მე ახლა  ვმუშაობ, ამ სოფელს ჰქვია ზუბი.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann146" ANNOTATION_REF="ann143_flexid_48844f9f-948e-42ed-a45c-02f478e1554c">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>თვითონ ეს წარმომავლობა ამ სიტყვის, [თუ] საიდან მოვიდა ზუბი, დიდი ფიქრი არ უნდა ამას. რუსების შემოსვლის მერე უნდა იყოს [შემოსული ეს სიტყვა]. ეს ტერიტორია, სადაც ახლა სოფელია, ადრე ეს ყოფილა ხობისწყლის ნაპირი.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann554" ANNOTATION_REF="ann551_flexid_4928ebd0-2997-45e8-aa7f-a8b663f6c3f8">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ანუ დასახლება არ ყოფილა.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann611" ANNOTATION_REF="ann608_flexid_ca34ebe4-35f1-4be2-a854-7be636f641d5">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ვიღაც კაცს მიჰყავდა თურმე ურემი. უნახავს ვიღაც რუსი გამწარებული დარბის და [რომ] უკითხავს რა გინდაო, თუ რა გაწუხებსო, ამას უთქვამს ზუბი, ზუბიო (=კბილიო). კბილი სტკივებია.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1089" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1086_flexid_37f0693c-42a2-4292-a478-0d676248ec86">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>მაგრამ იმ დროს სოფელში რუსული არავინ არ იცოდა და ამ კაცის მიმართ არანაირი, ასე ვთქვათ, შემწეობა  ამ მეურმის მხრიდან არ ყოფილა.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1338" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1335_flexid_273b186d-97a7-475c-90dc-5b23c959c6c2">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>მაგრამ თვითონ ეს სახელი, ზუბი [რადგანაც] უცხო სიტყვა იყო, ბოლოს იმ უბნისთვის დაურქმევიათ, სადაც დღევანდელი ჩვენი [თანა]სოფლელები ცხოვრობენ.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1596" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1593_flexid_0e95f1cc-ada9-40f8-93d1-929f7a6f952b">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>სკოლა არის ზუბში.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1660" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1657_flexid_bb65b0c4-71e1-4aac-885e-97baab6eeffc">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>შესაკრები [შესაკრებად] მაღაზია ცალკე გვაქვს .</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1732" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1729_flexid_592da25b-98e9-4e43-b2ad-b146657ad36d">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ადრე აფთიაქიც გვქონდა, მაგრამ არ ჰყავს იმდენი, ასე ვთქვათ, მომხმარებელი და  დაიკეტა.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1910" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1907_flexid_ff20def0-f051-491f-9617-297c09fb5d7d">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ყველაფერი რაც ქართულ წესებს ახასიათებს, ამ სოფელში - ყველაფერი სრულდება.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann2080" ANNOTATION_REF="ann2077_flexid_223b9763-1c4e-458e-8538-c2ca5ff9217e">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ახალი წლის შემოსვლა, ქრისტეშობის აღნიშვნა [აღინიშნება].</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
    </TIER>
    <TIER LANG_REF="xmf-fonipa" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="phrase-item"
        PARENT_REF="A_phrase-txt-xmf" TIER_ID="A_phrase-gls-xmf-fonipa">
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann6" ANNOTATION_REF="ann2_flexid_96c14b2e-6a18-42ac-aa4e-4b716af5fb06">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>tvitɔn ɑsɛ mɑ sɔdɛt muvʃɛnkin, tɛ sɔpɛls d͡ʒɔxɔ zubi.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann147" ANNOTATION_REF="ann143_flexid_48844f9f-948e-42ed-a45c-02f478e1554c">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>tvitɔn tɛ t͡sʼɑrmɔmɑvlɔbɑ tɛ sitʼqʼvɑʃi, sɔvrɛ mɔrtu zubikin, didi pikri vɑkʼɔ tɛs, rusɛpiʃ muʃulɑʃ ukʼuli ɔkʼɔ rdɑs dɔ tɛ tʼɛritʼɔriɑ, ɑdrɛ, ɑ, sɔdɛt ɑsɛ sɔpɛliɛn, tɛnɑ ʔɔpɛ xɔbt͡sʼqʼɑrpʼid͡ʒi.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann555" ANNOTATION_REF="ann551_flexid_4928ebd0-2997-45e8-aa7f-a8b663f6c3f8">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ɑnu dɑsɑxlɛbɑ vɑʔɔpɛ.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann612" ANNOTATION_REF="ann608_flexid_ca34ebe4-35f1-4be2-a854-7be636f641d5">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ɔdɔ midɡɑrɛni kʼɔs minɔʔvɛ urɛmi, ɔdɔ kud͡ziru rusi midɡɑrɛni ɡɑnt͡sʼɑrɛbuli ɡilɛrulɛ dɔ kɔukʼitxir mu ɡɔkʼɔniɑ, tu mu ɡɑt͡sʼuxɛnsiɑn, tɛs utkuɑl zubi, zubiɑ dɔ kʼibirs nɔt͡ʃʼuɛ.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1090" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1086_flexid_37f0693c-42a2-4292-a478-0d676248ec86">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>mɑrɑ indrɔs rusuli sɔpɛls mitins vɑut͡ʃkudu, ɔdɔ tɛ kʼɔt͡ʃʃɑ xɔlɔ mutuni, ɑsɛ vtkvɑt, ʃɛnt͡sʼɛbɑ tɛ mɛurɛmɛʃi ɡɑnʃɛ vɑʔɔpɛ.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1339" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1335_flexid_273b186d-97a7-475c-90dc-5b23c959c6c2">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>mɑrɑ tvitɔn tɛ sɑxɛli zubi ut͡sxɔ sitʼqʼvɑ rduni, bɔlɔs ɛti ubɑnʃɑ kiɡudvɑlunɑ, sɔdɛt ɑmdɣɑri t͡ʃkini sɔplɛlɛpi t͡sxɔvrɛnɑni.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1597" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1593_flexid_0e95f1cc-ada9-40f8-93d1-929f7a6f952b">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>skʼɔlɑ rɛ zubisi.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1661" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1657_flexid_bb65b0c4-71e1-4aac-885e-97baab6eeffc">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ɔʃɑqʼɑrɑli mɑɣɑziɑ t͡sɑlkʼɛ miɣunɑ.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1733" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1729_flexid_592da25b-98e9-4e43-b2ad-b146657ad36d">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ɑdrɛ ɑptiɑki xɔlɔ miɣudɛs mɑrɑ vɑʔuns izmɑ, ɑsɛ vtkvɑt, mɔmxmɑrɛbɛli dɔ iʃ dikʼilu.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann1911" ANNOTATION_REF="ann1907_flexid_ff20def0-f051-491f-9617-297c09fb5d7d">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>iirpɛli mut kɔrtul t͡sʼɛsɛns ɑxɑsiɑtɛnsin tɛ sɔpɛliʃ dinɑxɑlɛ, irpɛli isrulɛbu.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <REF_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="ann2081" ANNOTATION_REF="ann2077_flexid_223b9763-1c4e-458e-8538-c2ca5ff9217e">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ɑxɑli t͡sʼɑnɑʃi mulɑ, kirsɛʃi ɑɣniʃvnɑ.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </REF_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
    </TIER>
